data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this this move-in ready gem with a new furnace and AC for year-round comfort. It features an updated kitchen and new flooring in main areas, with materials ready for bedroom floors, allowing personal touch. Former wood-paneled dining now boasts modern drywall. Ideal for first-time buyers or downsizers. Don't miss out on this cozy, modern haven! Contact us to make it yours!
